(11, 1, '2014-04-01 15:20:51', '2014-04-01 19:20:51', 'At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we want every person who walks through our beauty school''s doors to feel welcome. Our school is always full of cosmetology students, instructors, guests, family members and friends, and that’s the way we like it. And once you graduate? We want our Orlo <a title="Alumni" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//alumni/" target="_blank">alumni</a> to keep in touch and remain a part of our community for many, many years.\r\n\r\nWe’re proud to be a part of the Capital Region community, and we enjoy <a title="Local Involvement" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/local-involvement/" target="_blank">being involved</a> in regional activities, from fundraisers to fashion shows. And we love when our neighbors come to us – our <a title="Student Salon Services" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/student-salon-services/" target="_blank">student salon services </a> are available throughout the week, and more visitors are always welcome!', 'Community', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'community', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:29:58', '2014-06-27 16:29:58', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
