(15, 1, '2014-04-01 15:21:23', '2014-04-01 19:21:23', 'Interested in applying for The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology’s program?\r\n\r\nWe’d love to meet you and discuss how our cosmetology school can help you move toward a successful career!\r\n\r\nFill out the form below with the preliminary information we need to start your application process. Once we review what you''ve submitted, we''ll move forward with in-person interviews, and finally, work with you to complete the full application process.', 'Apply Now', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'apply-now', '', '', '2014-06-26 17:16:30', '2014-06-26 21:16:30', '', 8, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
