(271, 2, '2014-04-15 12:53:48', '2014-04-15 16:53:48', 'At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we want every person who walks through our beauty school''s doors to feel welcome. Our school is always full of cosmetology students, instructors, guests, family members and friends, and that’s the way we like it. And once you graduate? We want our Orlo alumni to keep in touch and remain apart of our community for many, many years. \n\nWe’re proud to be a part of the Capital Region community, and we enjoy <a href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/local-involvement/" title="Local Involvement" target="_blank">being involved</a> in regional activities, from fundraisers to fashion shows. And we love when our neighbors come to us – our <a href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/student-salon-services/" title="Student Salon Services" target="_blank">student salon services </a> are available throughout the week, and more visitors are always welcome!\n', 'Community', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 12:53:48', '2014-04-15 16:53:48', '', 11, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/11-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(31, 1, '2014-04-01 15:48:55', '2014-04-01 19:48:55', 'Do you have questions for our admissions team? Or, would you like to visit The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology? You can reach our admissions team through the form below.\r\n\r\nIf you''d like to visit our cosmetology school, let us arrange a personal tour for you! We’ll show you around the classrooms and student salon at our cosmetology school, and sit with you to learn more about you, introduce ourselves and our program, answer any questions you may have about beauty school or the cosmetology industry, and discuss the admissions process. Tours are available Monday through Saturday - contact us today to schedule yours!\r\n\r\nWe’ll respond shortly to confirm your visit or answer any questions you may have about our program, teachers, students and school.', 'Contact Admissions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'contact-admissions', '', '', '2014-06-26 17:22:23', '2014-06-26 21:22:23', '', 8, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=31', 5, 'page', '', 0),
