(232, 2, '2014-04-14 17:30:27', '2014-04-14 21:30:27', 'Interested in visiting The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology? Let us arrange a personal tour for you! We’ll show you around our classrooms and student salon, and sit with you to learn more about you, introduce ourselves and our program, answer any questions you may have about our cosmetology school or the cosmetology industry, and discuss the admissions process.\r\n\r\nTours are available Monday through Saturday - contact us today to schedule yours!\r\n\r\nADD FORM\r\n\r\nWe’ll contact you shortly to confirm your visit.', 'Contact Admissions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 17:30:27', '2014-04-14 21:30:27', '', 31, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
