(48, 1, '2014-04-04 08:44:14', '2014-04-04 12:44:14', 'Students are most successful when they’re taught by individuals who are truly passionate about what they do. Our cosmetology school’s instructors teach based on years of their own experience in the cosmetology industry. With backgrounds as hairdressers, estheticians, nail technicians, make-up artists and more, our cosmetology professionals love what they do at our beauty school.', 'Our Staff', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'our-staff', '', '', '2014-06-26 17:13:33', '2014-06-26 21:13:33', '', 4, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=48', 3, 'page', '', 0),
