(50, 1, '2014-04-04 08:44:27', '2014-04-04 12:44:27', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is conveniently located at 232 North Allen Street, just a block from Central Avenue in Albany, New York. Easily accessible by local bus lines and interstates such as I-90 and I-87, our location has ample street parking upon arrival. Shopping centers, restaurants and other <a title="City Highlights" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/city-highlights/" target="_blank">city highlights</a> are close by, making our cosmetology school and the Capital Region enjoyable places to spend your days.\r\n\r\n[button url="https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Orlo+School+of+Hair+Design+And+Cosmetology/@42.673882,-73.784487,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89de0bae131e0663:0x5d238d52fbb58472"]Get Directions[/button]', 'Location', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'location', '', '', '2014-06-26 17:14:02', '2014-06-26 21:14:02', '', 4, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=50', 4, 'page', '', 0),
