(88, 1, '2013-09-18 12:00:45', '2013-09-18 16:00:45', 'We are very proud to announce that a graduate of The Orlo School of Hair Design &amp; Cosmetology, Robert Thomsen, is the winner of Milady''s Rising Star Video Contest. Robert''s focus on customer care and understanding of the importance of education in a stylists career has helped propel him to the top of the pack. In 2012, he was also recognized <a href="www.metroland.net">Metroland</a> as the Capital Region''s Best Stylist.\r\n\r\nRead more about Robert''s win and accolades on <em><a href="http://www.miladybeat.com/hairdresser-robert-thomsen-wins-miladys-rising-star-video-contest/">Milady Beat</a>.</em>', 'Alumni Spotlight: Orlo Alum, Robert Thomsen, Wins Milady''s Rising Star Video Contest', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'orlo-alum-wins-milady-contest', '', '\nhttp://www.miladybeat.com/hairdresser-robert-thomsen-wins-miladys-rising-star-video-contest/', '2014-06-30 16:46:01', '2014-06-30 20:46:01', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?p=88', 0, 'post', '', 0),
