(156, 1, '2014-04-11 09:33:35', '2014-04-11 13:33:35', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nHOW ORLO OFFERS CONTINUED CAREER ASSISTANCE TO ALUMNI\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Career Placement', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', 'career-placement', '', '', '2014-06-20 14:15:47', '2014-06-20 18:15:47', '', 13, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=156', 3, 'page', '', 0),
(280, 2, '2014-04-15 13:12:35', '2014-04-15 17:12:35', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nHOW ORLO OFFERS CONTINUED CAREER ASSISTANCE TO ALUMNI\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Career Placement', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '156-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 13:12:35', '2014-04-15 17:12:35', '', 156, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/156-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(290, 2, '2014-06-04 13:22:09', '2014-06-04 17:22:09', 'Passionate about cosmetology from a young age, Jackie spent 12 years as a hairstylist before she came to be an instructor at Orlo in 2012.  She loves her role instructing at this cosmetology school because “we teach them a trade that’s going to affect the rest of their lives.” She recalls her own life-changing moment after giving a young girl simple highlights. “It changed her whole attitude. It made her feel good about herself. She came back in with a bolder, more confident personality.”', 'Jackie Bushnell', 'Instructor', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jackie-bushnell', '', '', '2014-06-25 16:07:01', '2014-06-25 20:07:01', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?post_type=employee&#038;p=290', 0, 'employee', '', 0),
(292, 2, '2014-06-05 13:23:08', '2014-06-05 17:23:08', 'Determined to find a trade, Rosemarie began her career in beauty in 1971. Since then, it’s become much more than that. She began working with Rick Caputo in 1986, and moved with the Caputos to the current building in 1995. “If you love what you do, you never have to go to work. Not once in 30 years have I said, “Oh, I have to go to work…” Her passion carries through to another role, where she works in a salon once a week at a local senior citizen center. “It’s a fulfilling career,” she says, “You get to know and care for people.”', 'Rosemarie Craw', 'Instructor', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rosemarie-craw', '', '', '2014-06-25 16:07:08', '2014-06-25 20:07:08', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?post_type=employee&#038;p=292', 0, 'employee', '', 0),
