(288, 2, '2014-06-02 13:20:40', '2014-06-02 17:20:40', 'Lauren describes her preferred style as classic, neutral and spa-oriented. She began education at her Massachusetts cosmetology school in 2007, and she loves her role in creating a dynamic classroom for Orlo students. Describing Orlo, she says, “There’s a safe haven here – we’re structured, but we do a lot of fun things, too. We study advanced techniques that you might not see in a different beauty school.”', 'Lauren Bastille', 'Director of Education/Instructor', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lauren-bastille', '', '', '2014-10-02 10:45:22', '2014-10-02 14:45:22', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?post_type=employee&#038;p=288', 0, 'employee', '', 0),
(289, 2, '2014-06-03 13:21:09', '2014-06-03 17:21:09', 'Centered in the middle of three generations of stylists—her mother and her daughter—Jeanette knows the ins and outs of the industry. Licensed since 1982, her style is very versatile, catered to the client’s hair type, head shape, and their professionalism, all of which must be incorporated into their look. Her advice for potential students: “Cosmetology can take you through your whole life – it’s the type of work where you can adjust your schedule for full-time, or being a parent. This has been a business for a long time – it’s not going anywhere. Look for a school with a history of a lot of successful graduates.”', 'Jeanette Brown', 'Instructor', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jeanette-brown', '', '', '2014-06-25 16:06:55', '2014-06-25 20:06:55', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?post_type=employee&#038;p=289', 0, 'employee', '', 0),
(405, 1, '2014-06-20 13:41:18', '2014-06-20 17:41:18', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nWe love the cosmetology industry, and we love introducing new students to the opportunities it provides us all. If you share our passion, we invite you to consider our employment opportunities.\r\n\r\nThe Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is always looking for qualified applicants for the following positions:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Faculty</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative staff</li>\r\n	<li>Custodial</li>\r\n	<li>Reception and support staff</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nTo learn more about how you could become of member of our staff, <a href="mailto:info@theorloschool.com">email</a> us your résumé and cover letter, along with any other materials you think would give us an understanding of your talents and strengths. Reach out to us at any time to introduce yourself!', 'Employment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '175-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-20 13:41:18', '2014-06-20 17:41:18', '', 175, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/175-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
