(175, 1, '2014-04-11 11:54:26', '2014-04-11 15:54:26', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nWe love the cosmetology industry, and we love introducing new students to the opportunities it provides us all. If you share our passion, we invite you to consider our employment opportunities.\r\n\r\nThe Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is always looking for qualified applicants for the following positions:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Faculty</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative staff</li>\r\n	<li>Custodial</li>\r\n	<li>Reception and support staff</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nTo learn more about how you could become of member of our staff, <a href="mailto:info@theorloschool.com">email</a> us your résumé and cover letter, along with any other materials you think would give us an understanding of your talents and strengths. Reach out to us at any time to introduce yourself!', 'Employment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'employment', '', '', '2014-06-20 13:41:18', '2014-06-20 17:41:18', '', 0, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=175', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(235, 2, '2014-04-14 17:32:54', '2014-04-14 21:32:54', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nWe love the cosmetology industry, and we love introducing new students to the opportunities it provides us all. If you share our passion, we invite you to explore our employment opportunities.\r\n\r\nBelow you’ll find our current job opportunities at The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology. Explore the descriptions and (EMAIL US) your résumé and cover letter, along with any other materials you think would give us an understanding of your talents and strength.\r\n\r\nDon’t see a position listed now that’s right for you but think you can make a difference at our school? Reach out to us at any time to introduce yourself, and we’ll keep you in mind for future opportunities.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Employment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '175-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 17:32:54', '2014-04-14 21:32:54', '', 175, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/175-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
