(200, 1, '2014-04-14 16:58:29', '2014-04-14 20:58:29', '[first-line]cos &amp;bull; me &amp;bull; tology[/first-line]\r\n\r\n[second-line](käzm&amp;#601;täl&amp;#601;j&amp;#275;) noun[/second-line]\r\n\r\n<strong>Cosmetology.</strong> It is an education that can be acquired at any age. It is an industry that''s always in demand. And it drives careers that allows people to be creative and interact with others, whether it''s their first day at cosmetology school or decades of industry experience later.', 'Home Page Extra', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '196-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 16:58:29', '2014-04-14 20:58:29', '', 196, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/196-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(201, 2, '2014-04-14 16:58:45', '2014-04-14 20:58:45', 'For the Caputo family, The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology feels just like home. It’s where owners Rick and Alice Caputo’s children Angela and Andrew did their homework after school, and it’s where they remain today as co-directors of the beauty school with their parents.\r\n\r\nThe Caputo family’s cosmetology and Capital Region roots go back decades, beginning at former sister cosmetology school the Colonna in the 1960s, where Rick was an instructor. Rick and Alice, a licensed cosmetologist and instructor after studying at the Colonna, purchased the beauty school in 1989 and became co-directors. Six years later, the couple purchased The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology and fused the two schools, moving all classes to Orlo’s North Allen Street location in Albany. \r\n\r\nOver the years, Orlo has helped thousands of students of all ages and experience levels earn their cosmetology licenses. The school has participated in Capital Region events, partnered with local organizations and launched the careers of many alumni who have gone on to own major businesses in upstate NY and nationwide.\r\n\r\nToday, you can find Rick, Alice, Angela and Andrew actively involved in every aspect of the school’s day-to-day management. Visit Orlo in person and you’ll find them giving tours, helping students with guest services, instructing, answering phone calls - you name it! And if they’re not at the school, they’re probably at Studio Orlo, their Niskayuna salon.\r\n\r\n', 'History', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 16:58:45', '2014-04-14 20:58:45', '', 44, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/44-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(202, 2, '2014-04-14 17:01:28', '2014-04-14 21:01:28', '<strong>The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology</strong> is accredited by the National Accrediting Commission of Career Arts and Sciences, which is recognized by the United States Department of Education as the official accrediting agency for Hairdressing and Cosmetology schools. \r\n\r\nNational Accrediting Commission of Career Arts & Sciences (NACCAS)\r\n4401 Ford Avenue, Suite 1300\r\nAlexandria, VA 22302 - (703) 600-7600\r\n\r\n<h3>Orlo is licensed by:</h3>\r\n\r\nThe New York State Education Department\r\nOffice of Adult Career and Continuing Education Services (ACCES)\r\nBureau of Proprietary School Supervision\r\n99 Washington Avenue, Room 1613 OCP\r\nAlbany, NY 12234 - (518) 474-3969\r\n\r\n<h3>Orlo is approved by:</h3>\r\n\r\nUSDOE: United States Department of Education, authorizing participation in Title IV Federal Student Financial Assistance Programs.\r\n\r\nVA: New York State Division of Veteran’s Affairs.\r\n\r\nACCES-VR: New York State Education Department Office of Adult Career Continuing Education Services-Vocational Rehabilitation.\r\n\r\nNYHESC: Eligible Institution under the New York State Higher Education Services Corporation.\r\n\r\n<h3>Orlo is affiliated with:</h3>\r\n\r\nNYDOS: New York Department of State\r\n\r\nAACS: American Association of Cosmetology Schools\r\n\r\nCEA: Cosmetology Educators of America\r\n\r\nNYSBSA: New York State Beauty School Association\r\n\r\nBBB: Better Business Bureau\r\n\r\nNASFAA: National Association of Student Financial Aid Administrators\r\n', 'Accreditation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 17:01:28', '2014-04-14 21:01:28', '', 46, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/46-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(203, 2, '2014-04-14 17:03:10', '2014-04-14 21:03:10', 'Students are most successful when they’re taught by individuals who are truly passionate about what they do. Our cosmetology school’s instructors teach based on years of their own experience in the cosmetology industry. With backgrounds as hairdressers, nail technicians, make-up artists and more, our cosmetology professionals love what they do at our beauty school. \r\n\r\nMeet them online - and <a href="http://www.theorloschool.com//admissions/contact-admissions/" title="Contact Admissions" target="_blank">meet them in-person</a>!\r\n', 'Our Staff', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '48-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-14 17:03:10', '2014-04-14 21:03:10', '', 48, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/48-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
