on title="Absenteeism"]Extra charges may be incurred by students not completing the program on or before the scheduled date as stated on the enrollment agreement, which allows for up to 10% absenteeism. Hours still needed to complete the program after the scheduled completion date will be charged to the student at the rate of $10.30 per hour. Arrangements to satisfy these charges must be made before a student is allowed to continue. A subsequent addendum agreement for the remaining hours will be executed and a new graduate date will be determined with a 5% allowance for absences.\r\n[/accordion]', 'Tuition & Financial Aid', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 12:46:44', '2014-04-15 16:46:44', '', 27, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
