h her great team.  She couldn’t stress enough how awesome, trustworthy and well educated her team was.  Our very own Orlo Instructor, Ms. Jackie Bushnell, is a proud employee.\r\n\r\nThe best thing about being a hairstylist for Lauren is that the industry is pretty flexible, it’s not your typical nine to five job.  You can have a family, make your own schedule, be creative and free-spirited.  For the talented Lauren it fit her personality and lifetstyle!  We love Lauren!\r\n\r\nCome visit the lovely and talented team at <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Hair-Em-Salon/137550972979928">The Hair-Em Salon</a>, a full-service family salon conveniently located on 152 Main Street in Ravena, New York.  They offer hair care, nail care, tanning, waxing, wedding and prom packages.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theorloschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/10264139_679328319467_8981207446077766177_o.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-468" src="http://www.theorloschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/10264139_679328319467_8981207446077766177_o-300x194.jpg" alt="10264139_679328319467_8981207446077766177_o" width="300" height="194" /></a>', 'Alumni Spotlight: Lauren Sebert, Stylist/Salon Owner at Hair-Em Salon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '466-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 15:40:36', '2014-06-30 19:40:36', '', 466, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/466-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
