(477, 2, '2014-06-30 16:39:13', '2014-06-30 20:39:13', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology and other small businesses on North Allen in Albany are sprucing up, and giving the neighborhood a nice facelift while they''re at it. Orlo and a handful of other family business in the neighborhood all made improvements to their exteriors, investing well over a million dollars collectively in this mini-business district off Central Avenue.\r\n\r\nRead more about the upgrades on the Central Avenue BID''s blog, <a href="http://www.centralbidnewsletter.com/2014/01/family-businesses-join-together-to.html"><em>Blogging the Avenue</em></a>.', 'Orlo and North Allen Family Businesses Upgrade Neighborhood', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '91-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 16:39:13', '2014-06-30 20:39:13', '', 91, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/91-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(478, 2, '2014-06-30 16:39:50', '2014-06-30 20:39:50', 'We are very proud to announce that a graduate of The Orlo School of Hair Design &amp; Cosmetology, Robert Thomsen, is the winner of Milady''s Rising Star Video Contest. Robert''s focus on customer care and understanding of the importance of education in a stylists career has helped propel him to the top of the pack. In 2012, he was also recognized <a href="www.metroland.net">Metroland</a> as the Capital Region''s Best Stylist.\r\n\r\nRead more about Robert''s win and accolades on <em><a href="http://www.miladybeat.com/hairdresser-robert-thomsen-wins-miladys-rising-star-video-contest/">Milady Beat</a>.</em>', 'Orlo Alum Wins Milady''s Rising Star Video Contest', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 16:39:50', '2014-06-30 20:39:50', '', 88, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(479, 2, '2014-06-30 16:40:12', '2014-06-30 20:40:12', 'Check out this "Small Business Saturday" feature on the <em>Albany Times Union</em>''s "Albany" blog, written by Molly Belmont of the Central Avenue BID.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://blog.timesunion.com/albany/small-business-saturday-the-orlo-school/9101/">Small Business Saturday: The Orlo School </a>', 'Small Business Saturday: The Orlo School of Hair Design & Cosmetology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 16:40:12', '2014-06-30 20:40:12', '', 1, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(480, 2, '2014-06-30 16:40:39', '2014-06-30 20:40:39', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology has always given back--and now it''s being recognized for it. On April 30, the Neighborhood Resource Center will present its 2013 Outstanding Neighborhood Service awards at the Albany Housing Authority Atrium. Recipients include Rick and Alice Caputo, owners of The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology.\r\n<pre>The Orlo School will receive the Outstanding Local Retail Business Award for their tireless support of neighbors in their Beverwyck Neighborhood.</pre>\r\nRead more on the Central Avenue BID''s e-newsletter, <a href="http://www.centralbidnewsletter.com/2013/04/neighborhood-resource-center-presents.html"><em>Blogging the Avenue</em>.</a>', 'Orlo Receives "Outstanding Local Business" Award', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 16:40:39', '2014-06-30 20:40:39', '', 97, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/97-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(481, 2, '2014-06-30 16:40:44', '2014-06-30 20:40:44', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design &amp; Cosmetology has always given back--and now it''s being recognized for it. On April 30, the Neighborhood Resource Center will present its 2013 Outstanding Neighborhood Service awards at the Albany Housing Authority Atrium. Recipients include Rick and Alice Caputo, owners of The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology.\r\n<pre>The Orlo School will receive the Outstanding Local Retail Business Award for their tireless support of neighbors in their Beverwyck Neighborhood.</pre>\r\nRead more on the Central Avenue BID''s e-newsletter, <a href="http://www.centralbidnewsletter.com/2013/04/neighborhood-resource-center-presents.html"><em>Blogging the Avenue</em>.</a>', 'Orlo Receives "Outstanding Local Business" Award', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 16:40:44', '2014-06-30 20:40:44', '', 97, 'http://www.theorloschool.com/2014/06/97-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
