he Beauty Professional!\r\n\r\n<strong>KETT Cosmetics</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.kettcosmetics.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.kettcosmetics.com/</a>\r\nAirbrush Makeup for the digital Age!\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional Beauty Association</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.probeauty.org/" target="_blank"> http://www.probeauty.org/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Matter Of Trust</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.matteroftrust.org" target="_blank"> www.matteroftrust.org</a>\r\nRecycled hair clippings help save our environment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Modern Salon</strong>\r\n<a href="http://modernsalon.com/" target="_blank"> http://modernsalon.com/</a>\r\nYour Source for the latest trends in Hair Styles.\r\n\r\n<strong>International Beauty Show NYC</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.ibsnewyork.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.ibsnewyork.com/</a>\r\nHundreds of comprehensive classes, in-booth demonstrations and stellar main stage performances!\r\n\r\n<strong>Campus Habitat</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.campushabitat.com" target="_blank"> www.campushabitat.com</a>\r\nStudent housing company located in Troy NY with a wide variety of apartments from studios to 8 bedroom houses. Located just off 787 only minutes from Orlo. Contact the leasing office at 518-203-1430 for more information.', 'Resources', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'resources', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:34:13', '2014-06-27 16:34:13', '', 6, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=130', 4, 'page', '', 0),
