(425, 1, '2014-06-25 11:29:38', '2014-06-25 15:29:38', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is conveniently located at 232 North Allen Street, just a block from Central Avenue in Albany, New York. Easily accessible by local bus lines and interstates such as I-90 and I-87, our location has ample street parking upon arrival. Shopping centers, restaurants and other <a title="City Highlights" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/city-highlights/" target="_blank">city highlights</a> are close by, making our cosmetology school and the Capital Region enjoyable places to spend your days.\r\n\r\n[button url="https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Orlo+School+of+Hair+Design+And+Cosmetology/@42.673882,-73.784487,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89de0bae131e0663:0x5d238d52fbb58472"]Get Directions[/button]', 'Location', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-25 11:29:38', '2014-06-25 15:29:38', '', 50, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(251, 2, '2014-04-15 09:13:13', '2014-04-15 13:13:13', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is conveniently located at 232 North Allen Street, just a block from Central Avenue in Albany, New York. Easily accessible by local bus lines and interstates such as I-90 and I-87, our location has ample street parking upon arrival. Shopping centers, restaurants and other <a title="City Highlights" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/city-highlights/" target="_blank">city highlights</a> are close by, making our cosmetology school and the Capital Region enjoyable places to spend your days.\r\n\r\n[button url="https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Orlo+School+of+Hair+Design+And+Cosmetology/@42.673882,-73.784487,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89de0bae131e0663:0x5d238d52fbb58472"]Get Directions[/button]\r\n\r\n[button url="http://overit.com" color="purple"]Color Test[/button]', 'Location', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 09:13:13', '2014-04-15 13:13:13', '', 50, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(252, 2, '2014-04-15 09:20:30', '2014-04-15 13:20:30', 'Applying to colleges can be an exciting time, even if it’s a bit nerve-wracking. At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we know that choosing your cosmetology school is a big decision, and we understand if you’re a bit nervous about it. Our admissions team is prepared to answer any questions you may have about our beauty school, our program or our applications process at any time!\n\nOrlo accepts students on a rolling basis. <i>New classes begin every month!</i>\n<h3>Cosmetology Program Admission Requirements</h3>\nEach applicant must submit the following documents:\n<ul>\n	<li>Proof of age (the applicant must be 17 years of age) documented by a driver''s license, birth certificate, passport or other State or Federal ID</li>\n	<li>Copy of a high school diploma or GED</li>\n	<li>$100.00 non-refundable registration fee</li>\n	<li>All entrance documents (CLIENT MUST CONFIRM THIS LINE?)</li>\n	<li>Enrollment agreement</li>\n</ul>\nIn addition, all applicants must attend an interview and have a tour of our school prior to admission.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Admissions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 09:20:30', '2014-04-15 13:20:30', '', 8, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/8-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
