(140, 1, '2014-04-11 09:28:58', '2014-04-11 13:28:58', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nAt The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we mix classroom learning with hands-on practice of hairstyles, haircuts, manicures and more in our student salon. Our services are offered to Capital Region clients by our advanced students, supervised by our licensed and experienced instructors at all times.\r\n\r\nOur student salon is open:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday through Friday 10 a.m. – 3 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Monday, Wednesday and Thursday 6:30 p.m. – 10 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Saturday 9 a.m. – 2:30 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[accordion title="Cuts - All cuts include a wash and style"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Women''s Cut</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Men''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Children''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bang Trim</strong> - $3.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cut with Chemical Service</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Style"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Shampoo &amp; Roller Set</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Short Hair)</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Medium Hair)</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Long Hair)</strong> - $15.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Curling Iron Set</strong> - $12.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Formal Style</strong> - $15.00 - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Traditional Fingerwaves</strong> - $5.00 - $15.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>French Braids</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Braiding (Box, Cornrows, etc.)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Add-On Services - Prices added to cut, style, chemical or treatment service price"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Express Conditioning Treatment</strong> - $3.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Nioxin Shampoo Treatment</strong> - $3.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Flat Iron - Add on</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Long Hair - Add on</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Treatments"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Scalp Treatment</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Skin"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Facial</strong> - $15.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Nails"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Manicure</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Polish Change</strong> - $3.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>French Manicure</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pedicure</strong> - $15.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Makeup"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Makeup</strong> <strong>Application</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>False Eyelash Application</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Waxing"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Eyebrow</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Lip</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Color"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Short)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Medium)</strong> - $30.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Long)</strong> - $40.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Conditioning Color</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch + Color Balance</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bleach Retouch</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7"  - 1/3 Head</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7" - 2/3 Head</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7" - Whole Head</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - 1/3 Head</strong> - $25.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - 2/3 Head</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - Whole Head</strong> - $50.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Corrective Color</strong> - $50.00+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Texture"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Permanent Wave</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Spiral Permanent Wave</strong> - $40.00\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Perm Long Hair Add-On </strong>- $20.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Virgin Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Wave Nouveau</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Senior Citizens"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Shampoo &amp; Roller Set</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut and Roller Set</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSenior Citizen prices are honored Monday through Friday.\r\n[/accordion]\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Student Salon Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'student-salon-services', '', '', '2014-09-23 13:42:45', '2014-09-23 17:42:45', '', 11, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=140', 2, 'page', '', 0),
(277, 2, '2014-04-15 12:58:07', '2014-04-15 16:58:07', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nAt The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we mix classroom learning with hands-on practice of hairstyles, haircuts, manicures and more  in our student salon. Our services are offered to Capital Region clients by our advanced students, supervised by our licensed and experienced instructors at all times.\r\n\r\nOur student salon is open:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday through Friday 10 a.m. – 3 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Monday, Wednesday and Thursday 6:30 p.m. – 10 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Saturday 9 a.m. – 2:30 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(MENU OF SERVICES TO BE PROVIDED BY CLIENT)\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Student Salon Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '140-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 12:58:07', '2014-04-15 16:58:07', '', 140, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/140-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(278, 2, '2014-04-15 13:07:18', '2014-04-15 17:07:18', '<div id="lipsum">\n<p dir="ltr">The Capital Region is full of exciting opportunities, and The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is right in the middle of it all. With shopping destinations uptown, culture and night-life downtown, and fine dining options spread across the region, it’s hard to get bored.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">[accordion title="Dining"]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Even in short walking distance, you’ll find popular lunch spots like Pepper Jack’s, and on tough mornings, you can fuel up right around the corner at Dunkin Donuts. Branching out, you’ll find many hidden gems in the area, like New World Bistro on Delaware Avenue, and popular favorites like The Cheesecake Factory in Colonie Center. Central Avenue boasts many nearby options as well, such as Ichiban and El Mariachi. Whatever you’re in the mood for, Albany is sure to have it.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"> [/accordion]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">[accordion title="Entertainment"]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">The Capital Region is home to a variety of festivals and concerts all year long. From Tulip Fest in the spring to Pearl Palooza in the fall, there’s always something to look forward to. Even in the winter, you can get out and go ice-skating at Empire State Plaza or visit the nearby Adirondacks for many outdoor activities! Many big names come to perform in the area and surrounding local venues. Catch shows at Proctor’s or the Palace Theatre, or join your friends for a night out on Lark Street.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"> [/accordion]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">[accordion title="Shopping"]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">The Capital Region offers premier shopping at Crossgates Mall and Colonie Center, both less than five miles from our school. Wolf Road, Central Ave and Western Ave provide all the stores you need for everyday necessities.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">  [/accordion]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">[accordion title="Transportation"]</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Capital District Transit Authority (CDTA) provides an easy and inexpensive route system to get you where you need to go. Buses connect the entire region, including services extending north to Saratoga. Orlo is located four miles from the Albany-Rensselaer Amtrak rail station and six miles from the Albany International Airport.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"> [/accordion]</p>\n\n</div>', 'City Highlights', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-15 13:07:18', '2014-04-15 17:07:18', '', 142, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/142-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
