(438, 1, '2014-06-26 17:08:49', '2014-06-26 21:08:49', 'We love what we do at The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology.\r\n\r\nWe invite you to join us, learn from us and, most importantly, <em><strong>inspire us!</strong></em>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '118-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-26 17:08:49', '2014-06-26 21:08:49', '', 118, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/118-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(439, 1, '2014-09-23 13:44:55', '2014-09-23 17:44:55', '<div id="lipsum">\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UOLTgHadZD4\n\nAt The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we mix classroom learning with hands-on practice of hairstyles, haircuts, manicures and more in our student salon. Our services are offered to Capital Region clients by our advanced students, supervised by our licensed and experienced instructors at all times.\n\nOur student salon is open:\n<ul>\n	<li>Monday through Friday 10 a.m. – 3 p.m.</li>\n	<li>Monday, Wednesday and Thursday 6:30 p.m. – 10 p.m.</li>\n	<li>Saturday 9 a.m. – 2:30 p.m.</li>\n</ul>\n[accordion title="Cuts - All cuts include a wash and style"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Women''s Cut</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Men''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Children''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Bang Trim</strong> - $3.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Cut with Chemical Service</strong> - $5.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Style"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Shampoo &amp; Roller Set</strong> - $6.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Short Hair)</strong> - $6.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Medium Hair)</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Long Hair)</strong> - $15.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Curling Iron Set</strong> - $12.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Formal Style</strong> - $15.00 - $30.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Traditional Fingerwaves</strong> - $5.00 - $15.00</li>\n	<li><strong>French Braids</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Braiding (Box, Cornrows, etc.)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Add-On Services - Prices added to cut, style, chemical or treatment service price"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Express Conditioning Treatment</strong> - $3.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Nioxin Shampoo Treatment</strong> - $3.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Flat Iron - Add on</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Long Hair - Add on</strong> - $5.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Treatments"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Scalp Treatment</strong> - $10.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Skin"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Facial</strong> - $15.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Nails"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Manicure</strong> - $6.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Polish Change</strong> - $3.00</li>\n	<li><strong>French Manicure</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Pedicure</strong> - $15.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Makeup"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Makeup</strong> <strong>Application</strong> - $10.00</li>\n	<li><strong>False Eyelash Application</strong> - $5.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Waxing"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Eyebrow</strong> - $7.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Lip</strong> - $5.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Color"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Short)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Medium)</strong> - $30.00+</li>\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Long)</strong> - $40.00+</li>\n	<li><strong>Conditioning Color</strong> - $20.00+</li>\n	<li><strong>Retouch</strong> - $20.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Retouch + Color Balance</strong> - $35.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Bleach Retouch</strong> - $30.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7"  - 1/3 Head</strong> - $20.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7" - 2/3 Head</strong> - $30.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0"-7" - Whole Head</strong> - $40.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - 1/3 Head</strong> - $25.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - 2/3 Head</strong> - $35.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7"+ - Whole Head</strong> - $50.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Corrective Color</strong> - $50.00+</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Texture"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Permanent Wave</strong> - $20.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Spiral Permanent Wave</strong> - $40.00\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Perm Long Hair Add-On </strong>- $20.00</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li><strong>Virgin Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $40.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Retouch Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $30.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Wave Nouveau</strong> - $40.00</li>\n</ul>\n[/accordion][accordion title="Senior Citizens"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Shampoo &amp; Roller Set</strong> - $4.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry</strong> - $4.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Haircut</strong> - $4.00</li>\n	<li><strong>Haircut and Roller Set</strong> - $7.00</li>\n</ul>\nSenior Citizen prices are honored Monday through Friday.\n[/accordion]\n\n</div>', 'Student Salon Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '140-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-09-23 13:44:55', '2014-09-23 17:44:55', '', 140, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/140-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(440, 1, '2014-06-27 09:39:45', '2014-06-27 13:39:45', '<div id="lipsum">\r\n\r\nAt The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we mix classroom learning with hands-on practice of hairstyles, haircuts, manicures and more  in our student salon. Our services are offered to Capital Region clients by our advanced students, supervised by our licensed and experienced instructors at all times.\r\n\r\nOur student salon is open:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday through Friday 10 a.m. – 3 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Monday, Wednesday and Thursday 6:30 p.m. – 10 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Saturday 9 a.m. – 2:30 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[accordion title="Cuts - All Cuts Include a Wash and Style"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Women''s Cut</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Men''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Children''s Cut</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bang Trim</strong> - $3.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cut with Chemical Service</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Style"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Shampoo Set</strong> - $6.00, long hair - add on $5.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Short Hair)</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Medium Hair)</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blow-dry (Long Hair)</strong> - $15.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Curling Iron Set</strong> - $12.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Formal Style</strong> - $15.00 - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Traditional Fingerwaves</strong> - $5.00 - $15.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>French Braids</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Braiding (Box, Cornrows, etc.)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Treatments"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Scalp Treatment</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Color"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Short)</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Medium)</strong> - $30.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Whole Head Application (Long)</strong> - $40.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Conditioning Color</strong> - $20.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch + Color Balance</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bleach Retouch</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7  - 1/3 Head</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7 - 2/3 Head</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7 - Whole Head</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - 1/3 Head</strong> - $25.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - 2/3 Head</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - Whole Head</strong> - $50.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Corrective Color</strong> - $50.00+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Texture"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Permanent Wave</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Spiral Permanent Wave</strong> - $40.00, Long Hair Add On $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Virgin Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Wave Nouveau</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Nails"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Manicure</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>French Manicure</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pedicure</strong> - $18.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Makeup"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Makeup</strong> <strong>Application</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Waxing"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Eyebrow</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Lip</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Senior Citizens"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Shampoo Set/Blow-Dry</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut with Shampoo Set</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSenior Citizen prices are honored Monday through Saturday.\r\n[/accordion]\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Student Salon Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '140-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 09:39:45', '2014-06-27 13:39:45', '', 140, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/140-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(441, 1, '2014-06-27 12:14:47', '2014-06-27 16:14:47', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is accredited by the National Accrediting Commission of Career Arts and Sciences, which is recognized by the United States Department of Education as the official accrediting agency for Hairdressing and Cosmetology schools.\r\n\r\nNational Accrediting Commission of Career Arts &amp; Sciences (NACCAS)\r\n4401 Ford Avenue, Suite 1300\r\nAlexandria, VA 22302 - (703) 600-7600\r\n<h3>Orlo is licensed by:</h3>\r\nThe New York State Education Department\r\nOffice of Adult Career and Continuing Education Services (ACCES)\r\nBureau of Proprietary School Supervision\r\n99 Washington Avenue, Room 1613 OCP\r\nAlbany, NY 12234 - (518) 474-3969\r\n<h3>Orlo is approved by:</h3>\r\nUSDOE: United States Department of Education, authorizing participation in Title IV Federal Student Financial Assistance Programs.\r\n\r\nVA: New York State Division of Veteran’s Affairs.\r\n\r\nACCES-VR: New York State Education Department Office of Adult Career Continuing Education Services-Vocational Rehabilitation.\r\n\r\nNYHESC: Eligible Institution under the New York State Higher Education Services Corporation.\r\n<h3>Orlo is affiliated with:</h3>\r\nNYDOS: New York Department of State\r\n\r\nAACS: American Association of Cosmetology Schools\r\n\r\nCEA: Cosmetology Educators of America\r\n\r\nNYSBSA: New York State Beauty School Association\r\n\r\nBBB: Better Business Bureau\r\n\r\nNASFAA: National Association of Student Financial Aid Administrators', 'Accreditation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:14:47', '2014-06-27 16:14:47', '', 46, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/46-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(442, 1, '2014-06-27 12:15:09', '2014-06-27 16:15:09', 'The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is accredited by the National Accrediting Commission of Career Arts and Sciences, which is recognized by the United States Department of Education as the official accrediting agency for Hairdressing and Cosmetology schools.\r\n\r\nNational Accrediting Commission of Career Arts &amp; Sciences (NACCAS)\r\n4401 Ford Avenue, Suite 1300\r\nAlexandria, VA 22302 - (703) 600-7600\r\n<h3>Orlo is licensed by:</h3>\r\nThe New York State Education Department\r\nOffice of Adult Career and Continuing Education Services (ACCES)\r\nBureau of Proprietary School Supervision\r\n99 Washington Avenue, Room 1613 OCP\r\nAlbany, NY 12234 - (518) 474-3969\r\n<h3>Orlo is approved by:</h3>\r\nUSDOE: United States Department of Education, authorizing participation in Title IV Federal Student Financial Assistance Programs.\r\n\r\nVA: New York State Division of Veteran’s Affairs.\r\n\r\nACCES-VR: New York State Education Department Office of Adult Career Continuing Education Services-Vocational Rehabilitation.\r\n\r\nNYHESC: Eligible Institution under the New York State Higher Education Services Corporation.\r\n<h3>Orlo is affiliated with:</h3>\r\nNYDOS: New York Department of State.\r\n\r\nAACS: American Association of Cosmetology Schools.\r\n\r\nCEA: Cosmetology Educators of America.\r\n\r\nNYSBSA: New York State Beauty School Association.\r\n\r\nBBB: Better Business Bureau.\r\n\r\nNASFAA: National Association of Student Financial Aid Administrators.', 'Accreditation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:15:09', '2014-06-27 16:15:09', '', 46, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/46-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(443, 1, '2014-06-27 12:18:13', '2014-06-27 16:18:13', 'What drew Alice to the cosmetology industry? “It was the creative aspect of it and being able to work with my hands in a friendly atmosphere where they played good music all of the time. The salon atmosphere is the best.” With experience in the industry since 1978, Alice worked in salons and as a beauty school instructor before becoming a director of former sister school Colonna in 1989 then an owner/director of Orlo in 1995.\n\nShe loves seeing new people find a profession in which they can feel comfortable and can grow. It’s rewarding. Cosmetology is a journey and it’s always changing. You’re always learning new things and meeting new people, and she loves every minute of it.', 'Alice Caputo', 'Director/Owner', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '74-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:18:13', '2014-06-27 16:18:13', '', 74, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/74-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(444, 1, '2014-06-27 12:19:31', '2014-06-27 16:19:31', 'Whether you’re graduating high school now or trying to attend cosmetology school despite your current job keeping you busy, we know a weekday education schedule isn’t for everyone. At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, you can find the cosmetology classes you need held during weekdays, nights and weekends.\r\n\r\nOur full-time day, full-time evening and part-time evening programs provide students the flexibility they need to complete their studies on-time and on-budget.\r\n\r\n<strong>Full-time Day: </strong>\r\nMonday through Friday, 8:45 a.m. to 3:15 p.m.\r\n30 hours per week, approximately 34 to 36 weeks\r\n\r\n<strong>Full-time Evening:\r\n</strong>Monday through Thursday, 5:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m.\r\nSaturday: 9:00 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.\r\n25 hours per week, approximately 40 to 43 weeks\r\n\r\n<strong>Part-time Evening:\r\n</strong>Monday through Thursday, 5:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m.\r\n20 hours per week, approximately 50 to 54 weeks\r\n\r\n<a title="Tuition &amp; Financial Aid" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//admissions/tuition-financial-aid/" target="_blank">Tuition</a> is the same regardless of the program schedule you choose - we want you to choose the schedule that will provide you the opportunity to succeed!\r\n\r\n[accordion title="School Holidays"] No classes are scheduled at Orlo on the following days each year:\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New Year’s Day</li>\r\n	<li>Martin Luther King Day</li>\r\n	<li>Presidents’ Day</li>\r\n	<li>Memorial Day</li>\r\n	<li>Fourth of July (entire week)</li>\r\n	<li>Labor Day</li>\r\n	<li>Columbus Day</li>\r\n	<li>Veterans Day</li>\r\n	<li>Thanksgiving (two days)</li>\r\n	<li>Christmas (one week)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Unexpected Closures"] In cases of circumstances such as weather and natural disasters, school closure announcements will be available on our website. Additional notifications will be made by personal phone call, radio/TV announcements or on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/theorloschool" target="_blank">Facebook</a> as applicable.\r\n[/accordion]', 'Course Schedule', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '126-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:19:31', '2014-06-27 16:19:31', '', 126, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/126-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(447, 1, '2014-06-27 12:26:03', '2014-06-27 16:26:03', '<strong>FAFSA</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.fafsa.ed.gov" target="_blank"> www.fafsa.ed.gov</a>\r\nApply for financial aid online. Free application for federal student aid.\r\n\r\n<strong>NYS Division of Licensing</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.dos.state.ny.us/lcns/professions/appearance/appear.htm " target="_blank"> http://www.dos.state.ny.us/lcns/professions/appearance/appear.htm </a>\r\nYour source for New York State Appearance Enhancement Licensing info.\r\n\r\n<strong>Milady-Cengage</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.milady.cengage.com/index.asp" target="_blank"> http://www.milady.cengage.com/index.asp</a>\r\n#1 provider for cosmetology learning solutions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Milady Education Network</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.miladyednet.com/milady/Home" target="_blank"> http://www.miladyednet.com/milady/Home</a>\r\nOnline resource for networking, video tutorials and leading industry articles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Beauty Changes Lives</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.beautychangeslives.org" target="_blank"> http://www.beautychangeslives.org</a>\r\nA non-profit initiative designed to raise awareness of how careers in the hair, beauty and wellness industry transform lives both personally and professionally.\r\n\r\n<strong>Behind The Chair</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.behindthechair.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.behindthechair.com/</a>\r\nThis site is devoted to serving the professional salon industry with original content, resources, merchandise and education!\r\n\r\n<strong>WELLA</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.wellausa.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.wellausa.com/</a>\r\nWe proudly use WELLA PROFESSIONAL haircolor, an industry pioneer and favorite of hairstylists worldwide.\r\n\r\n<strong>Salon Today</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.salontoday.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.salontoday.com/</a>\r\nSalon Today is the leading business magazine for finer salon &amp; spa owners.\r\n\r\n<strong>American Salon</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.americansalonmag.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.americansalonmag.com/</a>\r\nCheck out the Latest Issue of American Salon Magazine Online!\r\n\r\n<strong>Cosmoprof</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.cosmoprofbeauty.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.cosmoprofbeauty.com/</a>\r\nProducts, Articles, Education &amp; Shows for the Beauty Professional!\r\n\r\n<strong>KETT Cosmetics</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.kettcosmetics.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.kettcosmetics.com/</a>\r\nAirbrush Makeup for the digital Age!\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional Beauty Association</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.probeauty.org/" target="_blank"> http://www.probeauty.org/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Matter Of Trust</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.matteroftrust.org" target="_blank"> www.matteroftrust.org</a>\r\nRecycled hair clippings help save our environment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Modern Salon</strong>\r\n<a href="http://modernsalon.com/" target="_blank"> http://modernsalon.com/</a>\r\nYour Source for the latest trends in Hair Styles.\r\n\r\n<strong>International Beauty Show NYC</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.ibsnewyork.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.ibsnewyork.com/</a>\r\nHundreds of Comprehensive Classes, In-Booth Demonstrations and Stellar Main Stage Performances!\r\n\r\n<strong>Campus Habitat</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.campushabitat.com" target="_blank"> www.campushabitat.com</a>\r\nWe are a student housing company located in Troy NY with a wide variety of apartments from studios to 8 bedroom houses. Located just off 787 only minutes from The Orlo School. Contact our leasing office at 518-203-1430 for more information.', 'Resources', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '130-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:26:03', '2014-06-27 16:26:03', '', 130, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/130-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2014-06-27 12:27:21', '2014-06-27 16:27:21', '<strong>FAFSA</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.fafsa.ed.gov" target="_blank"> www.fafsa.ed.gov</a>\r\nApply for financial aid online. Free application for federal student aid.\r\n\r\n<strong>NYS Division of Licensing</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.dos.state.ny.us/lcns/professions/appearance/appear.htm " target="_blank"> http://www.dos.state.ny.us/lcns/professions/appearance/appear.htm </a>\r\nYour source for New York State Appearance Enhancement Licensing info.\r\n\r\n<strong>Milady-Cengage</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.milady.cengage.com/index.asp" target="_blank"> http://www.milady.cengage.com/index.asp</a>\r\n#1 provider for cosmetology learning solutions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Milady Education Network</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.miladyednet.com/milady/Home" target="_blank"> http://www.miladyednet.com/milady/Home</a>\r\nOnline resource for networking, video tutorials and leading industry articles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Beauty Changes Lives</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.beautychangeslives.org" target="_blank"> http://www.beautychangeslives.org</a>\r\nA non-profit initiative designed to raise awareness of how careers in the hair, beauty and wellness industry transform lives both personally and professionally.\r\n\r\n<strong>Behind The Chair</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.behindthechair.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.behindthechair.com/</a>\r\nThis site is devoted to serving the professional salon industry with original content, resources, merchandise and education!\r\n\r\n<strong>WELLA</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.wellausa.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.wellausa.com/</a>\r\nWe proudly use WELLA PROFESSIONAL haircolor, an industry pioneer and favorite of hairstylists worldwide.\r\n\r\n<strong>Salon Today</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.salontoday.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.salontoday.com/</a>\r\nSalon Today is the leading business magazine for finer salon &amp; spa owners.\r\n\r\n<strong>American Salon</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.americansalonmag.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.americansalonmag.com/</a>\r\nCheck out the Latest Issue of American Salon Magazine Online!\r\n\r\n<strong>Cosmoprof</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.cosmoprofbeauty.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.cosmoprofbeauty.com/</a>\r\nProducts, Articles, Education &amp; Shows for the Beauty Professional!\r\n\r\n<strong>KETT Cosmetics</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.kettcosmetics.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.kettcosmetics.com/</a>\r\nAirbrush Makeup for the digital Age!\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional Beauty Association</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.probeauty.org/" target="_blank"> http://www.probeauty.org/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Matter Of Trust</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.matteroftrust.org" target="_blank"> www.matteroftrust.org</a>\r\nRecycled hair clippings help save our environment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Modern Salon</strong>\r\n<a href="http://modernsalon.com/" target="_blank"> http://modernsalon.com/</a>\r\nYour Source for the latest trends in Hair Styles.\r\n\r\n<strong>International Beauty Show NYC</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.ibsnewyork.com/" target="_blank"> http://www.ibsnewyork.com/</a>\r\nHundreds of comprehensive classes, in-booth demonstrations and stellar main stage performances!\r\n\r\n<strong>Campus Habitat</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.campushabitat.com" target="_blank"> www.campushabitat.com</a>\r\nWe are a student housing company located in Troy NY with a wide variety of apartments from studios to 8 bedroom houses. Located just off 787 only minutes from The Orlo School. Contact our leasing office at 518-203-1430 for more information.', 'Resources', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '130-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:27:21', '2014-06-27 16:27:21', '', 130, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/130-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
