 $20.00+</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch + Color Balance</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bleach Retouch</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7  - 1/3 Head</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7 - 2/3 Head</strong> - $30.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 0-7 - Whole Head</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - 1/3 Head</strong> - $25.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - 2/3 Head</strong> - $35.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Highlights 7+ - Whole Head</strong> - $50.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Corrective Color</strong> - $50.00+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Texture"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Permanent Wave</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Spiral Permanent Wave</strong> - $40.00, Long Hair Add On $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Virgin Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $40.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retouch Chemical Relaxer</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Wave Nouveau</strong> - $20.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Nails"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Manicure</strong> - $6.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>French Manicure</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pedicure</strong> - $18.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Makeup"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Makeup</strong> <strong>Application</strong> - $10.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Waxing"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Eyebrow</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Lip</strong> - $5.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion][accordion title="Senior Citizens"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Shampoo Set/Blow-Dry</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut</strong> - $4.00</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Haircut with Shampoo Set</strong> - $7.00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSenior Citizen prices are honored Monday through Saturday.\r\n[/accordion]\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Student Salon Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '140-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:31:10', '2014-06-27 16:31:10', '', 140, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/140-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(453, 1, '2014-06-27 12:32:32', '2014-06-27 16:32:32', 'At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we are thrilled to see our students graduate and move on to terrific new jobs in the cosmetology industry.\r\n\r\nBut that doesn’t mean we’re saying goodbye.\r\n\r\nOur alumni are active members of our cosmetology school''s community – helping current students find new jobs, visiting as special guest lecturers, even coming back to work as instructors.\r\n\r\nWe want our alumni to <a title="Involvement" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//alumni/involvement/" target="_blank">stay involved</a>, reach out for career assistance, and update us on current events and successes!', 'Alumni', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:32:32', '2014-06-27 16:32:32', '', 13, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(454, 1, '2014-06-27 12:37:26', '2014-06-27 16:37:26', 'Below are answers to some of The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology''s most frequently asked questions. If you have more questions for our team, feel free to contact us at any time.\n\n<b>When are the deadlines to apply?</b>\n\nWe have rolling admissions at Orlo, so there are no application deadlines. New classes begin every month!\n\n<b>What is the tuition for Orlo’s cosmetology program?</b>\n\nThe complete cost of our program is $12,000, including all fees and supplies.\n\n<b>How old do I need to be to apply at Orlo? Is there an age limit?</b>\n\nYou must be 17 years of age or older to apply. There is no age limit for entering our cosmetology program.\n\n<b>Is financial aid available?</b>\n\nYes it is. Find out opportunities and requirements on our <a title="Tuition &amp; Financial Aid" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//admissions/tuition-financial-aid/" target="_blank">tuition &amp; financial aid </a>page.\n\n<b>What is the job placement rate for Orlo graduates?</b>\n\nThe current job placement rate is 77 percent. You can find more information like this in our <a title="Student Disclosure" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//admissions/student-disclosure/" target="_blank">student disclosure</a>.\n\n<b>When are guest services available?</b>\n\nOur <a title="Student Salon Services" href="http://www.theorloschool.com//community/student-salon-services/" target="_blank">student salon</a> is open to the public Monday-Friday 10 a.m. to 3 p.m.; Monday, Wednesday and Thursday 6:30 p.m. to 10 p.m.; and Saturday 9 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '173-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 12:37:26', '2014-06-27 16:37:26', '', 173, 'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/06/173-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);

